          o The power cost has been decreased by 29%.<br />
          o This skill now teleports the Blademaster in the direction of movement at the time it is used, or forwards if there is no current movement.<br />
          o The skill prerequisite has been decreased to Onslaught rank 2.<br />
          o Path of Righteousness now applies damage bonuses correctly.<br />
